headline: NextEra Energy Plans Rate Changes and Solar Projects
summary: The latest update is out from NextEra Energy ( (NEE) ). Florida Power & Light Company has informed the Florida Public Service Commission of its plan to begin a base rate proceeding in 2025, aiming to implement a new four-year rate plan starting in 2026. The plan includes a significant increase in annual revenue requirements and proposals to fund solar and battery projects, potentially impacting the company’s financial operations and stakeholder interests. More about NextEra Energy NextEra Energy
